videos.description: Detroit Mercy's Dwayne Rose Jr. saves the day with his defense as he swats Foster Loyer's layup attempt out of bounds with ferocity.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dwayne Rose comes up with monster block vs. Michigan State) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dwayne Rose comes up with monster block vs. Michigan State

videos.description: Michigan State's A.J. Hoggard drives along the baseline and finds the contact as he goes up to finish a difficult layup in the paint and go to the line for one more.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (A.J. Hoggard draws contact for and-1 finish for Spartans) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: A.J. Hoggard draws contact for and-1 finish for Spartans

videos.description: Michigan State's Gabe Brown saves the day as he shuts down the Detroit Mercy layup attempt by tossing it off the backboard and out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Spartans' Gabe Brown comes up with huge block) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Spartans' Gabe Brown comes up with huge block

videos.description: Michigan State gains momentum as Gabe Brown sinks a 3-pointer in the corner to increase the Spartans' lead to 76-70 and force Detroit Mercy to call a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gabe Brown's 3 forces Detroit Mercy timeout) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gabe Brown's 3 forces Detroit Mercy timeout
